## EXPORT REQUIREMENTS

Every APPROVED clip must be prepared for export with:

- post_id
- final timestamp range
- duration (seconds)
- aspect_ratio = 9:16
- file name format: post_id_platform_version.mp4

---

## PIPELINE EXTENSION

After APPROVAL:

7. TRIM → cut clip using timestamp range  
8. FORMAT → convert to 9:16 if needed  
9. EXPORT → generate final file  
10. SCHEDULE → send to Buffer (manual or API)  

---

## SYSTEM LIMITATION (CURRENT)

- System identifies and prepares clips
- System does NOT yet automatically trim video
- System does NOT yet push to Buffer automatically
